{"type":"message","id":"8367d65d","parentId":"d517029b","timestamp":"2026-04-28T03:10:12.397Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking about LM Studio - they've added a model in LM Studio but the model dropdown menu on the page hasn't updated. They want to know how to add it.\n\nThis is about LM Studio (the desktop app), not about OpenClaw's model configuration. Let me think about what LM Studio does:\n\nIn LM Studio, when you download or add a new model, you typically need to:\n1. Go to the \"Local Server\" or chat tab\n2. The model selector should show all loaded models\n3. Sometimes you need to reload/refresh the model list\n\nBut wait - the user might be asking about OpenClaw's model configuration, not LM Studio specifically. Let me re-read: \"我的llm studio中增加了模型\" - they added a model in their LM Studio, but the page's dropdown menu didn't add it.\n\n\nI'm realizing there are two possible interpretations here - they could be referring to LM Studio's own interface where the model selector isn't updating after adding a new model, or they might be asking about OpenClaw's model configuration where newly added LM Studio models aren't showing up in the dropdown. The context suggests they're working within LM Studio itself, so I should focus on how to refresh or reload the model list there.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n在 LM Studio 里加了模型但下拉菜单没更新，通常有几种情况：\n\n**1. 模型还没被 LM Studio 识别**\n- 确认模型文件放在 LM Studio 的 models 目录里（通常在 `~/.lmstudio/models` 或 LM Studio 设置里指定的路径）\n- 文件要是 `.gguf`、`.safetensors` 等 LM Studio 支持的格式\n- 如果是从外部文件夹添加的，确认 LM Studio 的\"Models directory\"设置包含了那个路径\n\n**2. 需要手动刷新/重载**\n- 切到 **Local Server**（本地服务器）标签页\n- 点击模型选择器旁边的 **刷新/重载** 按钮\n- 或者完全关闭再重新打开 LM Studio\n\n**3. 模型格式不支持**\n- 检查模型格式是否在 LM Studio 支持列表中（GGUF、GGML 等）\n\n你说的\"页面上的下拉菜单\"是指 **LM Studio 应用内的下拉菜单** 还是 **OpenClaw 的配置页面**？如果是后者（OpenClaw 调用 LM Studio 的模型列表），那是另一个问题——需要在 OpenClaw 配置里指定 LM Studio 的 API endpoint 和模型名称。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"lm_studio","model":"qwen3.6-35b-a3b-q4_k_m","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777345729088,"responseId":"chatcmpl-a867fwqze3s0ct3318wj80b"}}
